6... Bf5 {You want to complete the development and secure the center with ... e6 , but first, you want to bring out the light-squared bishop. While ... Bg4 is very tempting and sometimes it will work like a charm, here it's not a good move.} ({We also mention the move} 6... Bg4 $2 {in the Mistakes to Avoid chapter.} 7. h3 Bh5 8. g4 Bg6 9. Bd2 {, and White develops a strong initiative.}) *

