14... Nd5 {Many players would take on d3 automatically because doubling the pawns is bad! Honestly, it's not – it's all about who controls the initiative and how many squares your pawns control. The pawn on f5 is great. Be open-minded!} (14... Bxd3 $6 15. Rxd3 {White suddenly develops a dangerous initiative.}) 15. Bxf5 exf5 16. Bd2 b5 {White's initiative on the kingside is much slower than Black's on the queenside.} *

