5... a6 {An important quality for a Scandinavian Defense practitioner is to be adaptive and look for unexpected opportunities – be open-minded. If White doesn't want to fight for the center, you can fight for some privileges yourself.} 6. Bd2 Qc5 7. Nge2 b5 8. Bb3 Bb7 {If you can, give your bishops the longest possible diagonals!} *

