8... e6 {Another moment where the wrong move order can cause Black major headaches.} (8... Qc7 $1 {. It's time to retreat.}) 9. d5 {A known move against the Scandi – with the black pawn on e7 it's not effective.} cxd5 10. Nxd5 Qc5 {Sadly, Black is too exposed on the queenside to enter this position.} 11. b4 Qc8 12. Nxf6+ gxf6 {Otherwise, Bb5 + will be a big problem.} 13. Nd4 Bg6 14. h4 h5 15. f4 {White is almost winning.} *

