8... Bxc2 {Don't even think about taking this pawn, at least very early in the opening phase when your king is in the center. The move has many problems, but in this position, White wins the game on the spot.} (8... Qc7 $1 {. It's time to retreat.}) 9. Nb5 Qb6 10. Nd6+ {This is one of the fundamental tricks in the Scandinavian Defense.} *

