10... Bg4 {This tempting move is borderline losing.} (10... Bg6 {is the only reasonable move.}) 11. f3 Bh5 12. g4 Bg6 13. g5 {This move feels positionally wrong as it weakens for White so many squares, but chess is a very concrete game. The problem is that the jump on d5 now is impossible.} Nh5 14. Bxe6 {White crashes through.} *

