ld be pretty annoying. The black king feels pretty safe in the center.} 19. c3 b5 20. Be4 Nb6 {Only now that Black has done everything to organize counterplay can they start thinking about their king's safety. Technically, the king is already safe on e8 , but the h8 -rook still needs to enter the game. Maybe at certain moments, ... Rh5 or ... Rh4 will be possible.} *

