 Qc1 Qxa5 {And the lost pawn is reclaimed.} ({After Rd1 , this is how the game might continue:} 22... Qf5 23. Ra3 Nb6 24. Bg4 Qf6 25. Rf3 Qd8 26. Be5 Bd5 {. White runs out of tricks.} 27. Bxg7 Kxg7 28. Nxb6 Qxb6 {, and Black is safe.}) *

