e5 Nxb7 Nxc4 Rc1! Very precise. Nxe3 Rxc7} Rf8 $1 {fxe3 f5} 13. Na5 {f4 . Black is in time with their own ideas.} Rc8 {Kd7 Rxf8 Bxf8 exf4 Bd6 . Even though Black is down a pawn, you should be able to keep the balance.} 14. g3 {e5 f5 e4 g4 Bc7 Nc4 Kc6 Kf2 Kd5 Ne3+ Kd4 , and Black is holding.}) *

