 {Black is simply faster than White.} 20. Qc3 Rhd8 {Black has successfully traded the dark-squared bishops, controls the d-file, and is ready to lift the knight to d4 . If you parry White's ideas with b2 - b4 - b5 , White might experience the effects of the "bad" bishop on f3 .} *

